<h2 id="3-longest-substring-without-repeating-characters">3. Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters</h2>
<p><strong>Difficulty: medium</strong></p>

<p>Given a string, find the length of the longest substring without repeating characters.</p>

<p><strong>Example 1:</strong></p>

<p>Input: â€œabcabcbbâ€
Output: 3 
Explanation: The answer is â€œabcâ€, with the length of 3.</p>

<p><strong>Example 2:</strong></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Input: â€œbbbbbâ€
Output: 1
Explanation: The answer is â€œbâ€, with the length of 1.</p>
</blockquote>

<p><strong>Example 3:</strong></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Input: â€œpwwkewâ€<br />
Output: 3<br />
Explanation: The answer is â€œwkeâ€, with the length of 3. <br />
Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Note that the answer must be a substring, â€œpwkeâ€ is a subsequence and not a substring.</p>
</blockquote>

